io.github.hhromic.uimr.stats

Class TopNTable<K extends Comparable<K>,V extends Comparable<V>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.hhromic.uimr.stats.TopNTable<K,V>

  • public class TopNTable<K extends Comparable<K>,V extends Comparable<V>>
extends Object
    This class handles a top-n data table.

    The K type defines the keys type and the V defines the values type. the top-n data table sorts its entries by value in descending order. For same values, the entries are then sorted by the key in ascending order.

    The top-n table is internally backed by a TreeSet object.

    Since:
    4.0
    Author:
    Hugo Hromic
